Content-Range.description:
Range of the returned resources formated as <range-start>-<range-end>/<size>, with:
- range-start: the index of the first resource in the list;
- range-end: the index of the last resource in the list;
- size: the total number of available resources (or '*' if unknown).
example: 200-300/67589

